{"tid":2319341,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"鬼滅 vs 死神","createTime":"2020-12-10T04:36:08.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-11T17:47:34.000Z","uid":275664,"like":285,"dislike":48,"uniUserReply":55,"replies":[{"pid":"65d299f92b227d23b39b60c8121e83a6cc5d3cab","tid":2319341,"uid":275664,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T04:36:08.000Z","msg":"成日都火影 vs 鬼滅<br />\n不如討論下2套都講係以 <br />\n人 vs 同人相似嘅物種<br />\n<br />\n死神有13隊<br />\n鬼滅有鬼殺隊<br />\n<br />\n死神就打完13隊後 13隊做埋隊友去打破面<br />\n大佬係藍染<br />\n利申無睇血戰編<br />\n<br />\n鬼滅就鬼殺隊vs 鬼<br />\n大佬係無慘<br />\n<br />\n動畫 無論係作畫 同情感牽動都係鬼滅好d<br />\n但死神去到破面篇d 伏筆 設定都足過鬼滅<br />\n<br />\n而漫畫作畫就唔洗講<br />\n死神一定型好多<br />\n<br />\n大家又中意邊套多d?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />死神<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />鬼滅"},{"pid":"e5fc5f0eeb84db2f727e6e0c160364f4da0dae64","tid":2319341,"uid":56550,"like":3,"dislike":23,"score":-20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T04:36:59.000Z","msg":"火影世界第一<br />\nSao世界第一"},{"pid":"cc9270bd7d63c6f9fd08f34838adadff158b8648","tid":2319341,"uid":40267,"like":51,"dislike":2,"score":49,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T04:37:40.000Z","msg":"鬼殺隊有十刃咁潮先講"},{"pid":"39da54291973bc5b61800fe3e2c644fe26e01bac","tid":2319341,"uid":162095,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T04:37:51.000Z","msg":"又鬼滅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d86d9a7ba8e31c76d97e8b311e1910c588c2d4a2","tid":2319341,"uid":61005,"like":19,"dislike":2,"score":17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-10T04:40:27.000Z","msg":"死神型在久保寫嘅對白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋久保人物塑造嘅能力點都唔係鬼滅可以比"},{"pid":"e9eef83b1d19309a883621c7d5b2f54a3c8b8463","tid":2319341,"uid":139173,"like":2,"dislike":5,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"cc9270bd7d63c6f9fd08f34838adadff15